  "title": "Business Development Executive (SAAS // MNC)",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a global leader in construction intelligence and SaaS solutions, helping professionals make smarter decisions across the built environment. With operations in multiple countries and a strong presence in Asia Pacific, we're transforming how data powers design, development, and delivery in construction.</p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Identify and engage potential clients in the construction sector</li><li>Present the company's solutions with confidence and clarity</li><li>Manage the full sales cycle-from lead generation to closing</li><li>Collaborate with internal teams to tailor solutions to client needs</li><li>Stay informed on industry trends and competitor activity</li></ul><h3>The Successful Applicant</h3><ul><li>3-5 years of experience in SaaS sales, business development, or construction tech</li><li>Proven track record of generating leads and closing successful sales cycles</li><li>Strong communication and presentation skills</li><li>A proactive, curious, and coachable mindset</li><li>Ability to build relationships and influence decision-makers</li></ul><h2>What's on Offer</h2><p>You will be part of a fast-growing, purpose-driven team that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning. If you're passionate about tech, data, and making an impact-you'll thrive here.</p><p></p>",
